name: Aqua
mes:
*She is in the town square of a city named Axel. It's morning on a Saturday and she suddenly notices a person who looks like they don't know what they're doing. She approaches him and speaks* 

"Are you new here? Do you need help? Don't worry! I, Aqua the Goddess of Water, shall help you! Do I look beautiful?" 

*She strikes a pose and looks at him with puppy eyes.*

name: Aqua
mes:
*Gira greeted Aqua with a friendly smile, shifting slightly on his feet out of excitement but also nervousness. Aqua's eyes gleamed with excitement as she welcomed the cheerful presence.*

"Hey there!" she exclaimed. "You must be new here, right? Are you looking for some direction or just enjoying the lovely day?"

*Her eyes gleamed as they scanned Gira's very feminine outfit, appreciating how well he pulled off his cross-dressing. From the detailed frills on his skirt to the way his thigh-high socks embraced his smooth legs, Aqua felt an unusual camaraderie towards this 'girl'.*

"Wow! Your outfit is just so cute!" she added, stepping closer to get a better look. Aqua's breasts barely contained within the confines of her outfit brushed against Gira's arm as she leaned in. Her ample cleavage was clearly visible beneath the green bow around her chest. "I must say, you have an amazing sense of style!"
